%% Diagram: Service Worker streaming response relay using TransformStream
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor Page
    participant SW as Service Worker
    participant Cache as Cache Storage
    participant Net as fetch (network)
    participant TX as TransformStream

    Page->>SW: GET /article (FetchEvent)
    SW->>SW: event.respondWith(new Response(readable))
    Note over SW,TX: SW returns immediately;<br/>response is alive but empty.
    SW->>Cache: match(/shell.html)
    Cache-->>SW: cached shell ReadableStream
    SW->>TX: shell.body.pipeTo(writable, { preventClose: true })

    par
        SW->>Net: fetch(/api/article-body)
    end
    Net-->>SW: Response (body stream)
    SW->>TX: body.pipeTo(writable)
    TX-->>Page: chunks delivered as they arrive
    Note over Page: First paint is the cached shell;<br/>article body streams in below.
